{"tid":897470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內地黃金桃充日本桃　兩水果商分別罰款3600及6000","createTime":"2018-11-11T02:38:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-11T04:13:08.000Z","uid":42188,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fa00baac3fafa3fe14a8a7e10e467767ecd713b5","tid":897470,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T02:38:04.000Z","msg":"兩名水果零售商將來自內地的黃金桃冒充成日本黃金桃出售，違反《商品說明條例》，今日(6日)分別在沙田裁判法院及西九龍裁判法院被判罰款3600港元及6000港元。 <br />\n<br />\n海關早前接獲舉報，指有水果零售商鋪出售附有虛假產地說明的黃金桃，海關人員其後採取試購行動，分別在馬鞍山及旺角兩間水果零售商檢獲共72個懷疑附有虛假日本產地說明的黃金桃。經調查後，發現有關黃金桃產自內地，與所聲稱的不符。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港小店<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"30b45f0b129da5b2f421f0dae54fbb16e975e381","tid":897470,"uid":3912,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T03:33:13.000Z","msg":"Royal級？"},{"pid":"596d509dcc43286c7c41a381d527b19f6274fe56","tid":897470,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30b45f0b129da5b2f421f0dae54fbb16e975e381","tid":897470,"uid":3912,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T03:33:13.000Z","msg":"Royal級？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T03:53:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ab313ebfab1b7e515b06fe16377e46548968eac","tid":897470,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"596d509dcc43286c7c41a381d527b19f6274fe56","tid":897470,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30b45f0b129da5b2f421f0dae54fbb16e975e381","tid":897470,"uid":3912,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T03:33:13.000Z","msg":"Royal級？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T03:53:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T04:13:08.000Z","msg":"特供畀領導<br />\n你地買唔到<img sr